魔戒三部曲的每一部電影都獲得MTV電影大獎的最佳電影獎及[[雨果獎|雨果獎]]最佳劇本的獎項。《魔戒現身》及《王者再臨》都獲得[[英國電影和電視藝術學院|英國電影和電視藝術學院]]的最佳電影獎項。《雙城奇謀》的聲帶不能獲得奧斯卡金像獎的提名，因條例禁止前作含音樂的聲帶被提名，而這條例在《王者再臨》被提名時已被廢除，故《王者再臨》可獲得獎項。

=== 原著、電影差異的反響 ===

魔戒電影三部曲廣為人所接受，但一些魔戒小說的讀者不滿改編電影所作出的變動<ref name="Anticipation">{{cite web |language=en |publisher=The University of Oklahoma |title=The Mines of Moria: ‘Anticipation’ and ‘Flattening’ in Peter Jackson’s The Fellowship of the Ring |url=http://faculty-staff.ou.edu/C/Janet.B.Croft-1/anticipationandflattening.htm |author=Janet Brennan Croft |date=02-2003 |accessdate=11-09-2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111031065417/http://faculty-staff.ou.edu/C/Janet.B.Croft-1/anticipationandflattening.htm |archivedate=2011-10-31 }}</ref>。角色如[[甘道夫|甘道夫]]、[[亞拉岡|亞拉岡]]、[[亞玟|亞玟]]、[[迪耐瑟二世|迪耐瑟]]、[[法拉墨|法拉墨]]、[[金靂|金靂]]甚至主角[[佛羅多·巴金斯|佛羅多·巴金斯]]的一些改動及情節的差異（如精靈參與[[聖盔谷之戰|聖盔谷之戰]]及法拉墨將哈比人帶到[[奧斯吉力亞斯|奧斯吉力亞斯]]）被認為改變了原著原來的風格及主題思想。

有許多人非議改編電影將[[臨水之戰|臨水之戰]]刪去，托爾金書迷認為這部分相當重要<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = Arthedain.netfirms.com | title = Irrelevant and Anticlimactic? The "Scouring" Considered, for Readers and Others | url = http://arthedain.netfirms.com/scouring.html | accessdate = 11-09-2009 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080706053923/http://arthedain.netfirms.com/scouring.html | archivedate = 2008-07-06 }}</ref>。

知名的托爾金學者韋恩·哈蒙德（Wayne Hammond）對魔戒三部曲的首兩部作出了以下的評論：

{{Cquote|我發現杰克逊的這兩部電影歪曲了原著……情節上只是基本忠於原著……刪減及縮短是必須的，但在沒有很好的理由之下，不要改動或添加一些新的元素……直到現時為止，電影裡取得了成功的地方都是依照托爾金原著的地方，而敗筆則是那些偏離了托爾金原著的部分，特別是在人物性格方面。電影裡的許多角色的個性都較原著陰暗和軟弱（特別是佛羅多），或侮辱地模仿原著角色（皮聘、梅里、金靂）……制片人犠牲了托爾金小說豐實的故事內容及角色性格，更別說那些不合情理的竄改、低級趣味、低級驚悚……許多的評論家都讚揚電影忠於原著，甚至超越原著，這就像在傷口上灑鹽，無法令人接受……<ref name="Anticipation" />}}

一些不滿改編電影的書迷釋出了他們修改版本電影，去除了許多電影作出的變更，使其更忠於原著。他們制作了一個合共八小時的魔戒三部曲版本，稱為《魔戒：純化版》<ref>{{cite web |language=en |publisher=The Cimmerian |title=Tolkien Purists Strike Back! |url=http://www.thecimmerian.com/?p=739 |author=Leo Grin |accessdate=11-09-2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071228132400/http://www.thecimmerian.com/?p=739 |archivedate=2007-12-28 }}</ref>。

魔戒電影三部曲的支持者則主張電影很好地詮釋了原著，絕大部分的變動也是必要的。許多的魔戒電影參與者本身也是魔戒小說的愛好者，[[基斯杜化·李|基斯杜化·李]]更曾與托爾金會面<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = IMDB | title = Christopher Lee | url = http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0000489/bio | accessdate = 11-09-2009 | archive-date = 2010-08-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100817025134/http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0000489/bio | dead-url = no }}</ref>，鮑恩斯認為不論怎麼，這只不過是他們對原著的詮釋<ref>''The Frodo Franchise: The Lord of the Rings and Modern Hollywood''，第68頁</ref>。傑克森也曾經說，如果只將原著簡化並放上銀幕只會把它弄糟，又說：「是的，電影並不是真正的《魔戒》，但這仍是很棒的電影。」<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = Members.tripod.com | title = 20 QUESTIONS WITH PETER JACKSON | url = http://members.tripod.com/peter_jackson_online/lotr/articles/20_questions.htm | accessdate = 11-09-2009 | archive-date = 2020-08-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200809030130/http://members.tripod.com/peter_jackson_online/lotr/articles/20_questions.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = The One Ring | title = The Complete List of Film Changes | url = http://www.theonering.com/landing_pages/25,3.html | accessdate = 11-09-2009 | archive-date = 2011-07-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110717020812/http://www.theonering.com/landing_pages/25%2C3.html | dead-url = yes }}</ref>其他的書迷也認為，電影即使出現了變動，這也是對原著的尊崇，去懇請那些沒有讀過原著的觀眾去閱讀。阿爾達百科全書（托爾金網上百科全書）寫道：

{{Cquote|向彼得·杰克逊及魔戒電影的工作致謝似乎是合適的，縱使他們的電影與原著的規模及錯綜複雜的事物並不太相近，要制作到與原著一致是不可能的，他們的電影依然是一部傑作。特別是彼得·杰克逊的制片人勇於去接受如此困難的挑戰並取得如此優秀的成果，應該受到欽佩。《魔戒》完整的故事是不可能電影化的，而彼得·杰克逊卻是能夠做得比任何人都接近的一個。<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = The Encyclopedia of Arda | title = The Return of the King： A Movie-goer’s Guide | url = http://www.glyphweb.com/ARDA/returnoftheking.html | accessdate = 11-09-2009 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111006165726/http://www.glyphweb.com/arda/returnoftheking.html | archive-date = 2011-10-06 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>}}

2005年，神話會社（Mythopoeic Society）出版了一卷收錄魔戒電影三部曲的評論文章及研究電影對流行文化所造成的影響的書籍，書名是《電影上的托爾金：評論[[彼得·杰克逊|彼得·傑克森]]的魔戒》<ref name="Essays">{{cite web | language = en | publisher = Mythopoeic Society | title = Tolkien on Film：Essays on Peter Jackson’s The Lord of the Rings | url = http://www.mythsoc.org/press/tolkien.on.film/ | accessdate = 11-09-2009 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090923204958/http://www.mythsoc.org/press/tolkien.on.film/ | archivedate = 2009-09-23 }}</ref>。這著作因其評論中肯、評論合理而備受好評，該書「尋求電影的成功之處及失敗之處，並找出電影被許多人讚揚及悲嘆的原因」<ref name="Essays" />。書裡的評論文章包含比較魔戒原著與電影對女性的取態、對支持電影的評論、評估原著與電影對英雄及英雄主義的看法異同。凱茜·阿科爾斯-喬丹、珍·錢斯、維多利亞·基杜斯克、莫琳·杜姆主張女性代表人物亞玟在電影裡雖與原著有所不同，但亦大抵忠於原著<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Cathy Akers-Jordan | title = ''Tolkien on Film: Essays on Peter Jackson’s The Lord of the Rings'' | chapter = Fairy Princess or Tragic Heroine? The Metamorphosis of Arwen Undomiel in Peter Jackson’s The Lord of the Rings Films | date = 2005年 | publisher = Altadena | isbn = 1887726098 }}</ref><ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Jane Chance | title = ''Tolkien on Film: Essays on Peter Jackson’s The Lord of the Rings'' | chapter = Tolkien’s Women (and Men): The Films and the Books | date = 2005年 | publisher = Altadena | isbn = 1887726098 }}</ref><ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Victoria Gaydosik | title = ''Tolkien on Film: Essays on Peter Jackson’s The Lord of the Rings'' | chapter = The Transformation of Tolkien’s Arwen and the Abandonment of the Psyche Archetype: The Lord of the Rings on the Page and on the Screen | date = 2005年 | publisher = Altadena | isbn = 1887726098 }}</ref><ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Maureen Thum | title = ''Tolkien on Film: Essays on Peter Jackson’s The Lord of the Rings'' | chapter = The “Sub-Subcreation” of Galadriel, Arwen, and Éowyn: Tolkien’s Women and The Lord of the Rings | date = 2005年 | publisher = Altadena | isbn = 1887726098 }}</ref>。大衛·布賴曼批評一些迴護電影的論點，諸如「這是傑克森的視角，不是托爾金的」、「他們已經很努力了」、「這為小說帶來了新讀者」、「完美的電影片長應該有四十小時」、「小說依然被放在書架上」等<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = David Bratman | title = ''Tolkien on Film: Essays on Peter Jackson’s The Lord of the Rings'' | chapter = Summa Jacksonica: A Reply to Defenses of Peter Jackson’s Lord of the Rings films, after St. Thomas Aquinas | date = 2005年 | publisher = Altadena | isbn = 1887726098 }}</ref>。他寫道：「[[彼得·杰克逊|彼得·傑克森]]對托爾金小說的理解力只有九歲小孩的程度」<ref name="RevolutionSF">{{cite web | language = en | publisher = RevolutionSF | title = Tolkien On Film | url = http://www.revolutionsf.com/article.php?id=2923 | author = Joe Crowe | accessdate = 11-09-2009 | archive-date = 2009-11-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20091129233156/http://www.revolutionsf.com/article.php?id=2923 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>，又將電影評價為「一等的視覺及道具、二等的獨立創作、三等的忠於托爾金原著、四等的表達托爾金精神及風格」<ref name="RevolutionSF" />。達恩·蒂蒙斯寫道，電影的主題被佛羅多的形象破壞，電影裡的佛羅多較原著軟弱<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Dan Timmons | title = ''Tolkien on Film: Essays on Peter Jackson’s The Lord of the Rings'' | chapter = Frodo on Film: Peter Jackson’s Problematic Portrayal | date = 2005年 | publisher = Altadena | isbn = 1887726098 }}</ref>。凱拉·麥金尼·威金斯認為，電影錯解了及曲解了托爾金小說所表達的英雄本質，這是電影將重點由角色的成長轉移到動作冒險的結果<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Kayla McKinney Wiggins | title = ''Tolkien on Film: Essays on Peter Jackson’s The Lord of the Rings'' | chapter = The Epic Hero and the Little Man | date = 2005年 | publisher = Altadena | isbn = 1887726098 }}</ref>。珍妮特·布倫南·克羅夫特批評電影的劇本，又比較托爾金小說的細膩與傑克森電影「太多太急」的傾向<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Janet Brennan Croft | title = ''Tolkien on Film: Essays on Peter Jackson’s The Lord of the Rings'' | chapter = Mithril Coats and Tin Ears: ‘Anticipation’ and ‘Flattening’ in Peter Jackson’s The Lord of the Rings Trilogy | date = 2005年 | publisher = Altadena | isbn = 1887726098 }}</ref>。

== 影響 ==

魔戒電影三部曲的上映及發行掀起了《魔戒》及托爾金相關著作的熱潮，大為提高了托爾金對流行文化的影響力<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = The Boston Globe | title = Lord of the Gold Ring | url = http://www.boston.com/news/globe/magazine/articles/2003/11/16/lord_of_the_gold_ring/ | author = Ethan Gilsdorf | date = 2003-11-16 | accessdate = 11-09-2009 | archive-date = 2006-08-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20060827073302/http://www.boston.com/news/globe/magazine/articles/2003/11/16/lord_of_the_gold_ring/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。有傳托爾金家族因電影三部曲而不和，[[克里斯托夫·托爾金|克里斯托夫·托爾金]]與西蒙·托爾金因對改編電影的觀點不同而反目<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = The New Zealand Herald | title = Feud over 'Rings' movie splits Tolkien family | url = http://www.nzherald.co.nz/lord-of-the-rings/news/article.cfm?c_id=594&objectid=231286 | date = 03-12-2001 | accessdate = 11-09-2009 | archive-date = 2011-08-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110805095910/http://www.nzherald.co.nz/lord-of-the-rings/news/article.cfm?c_id=594&objectid=231286 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[克里斯托夫·托爾金|克里斯托夫·托爾金]]否認有關的傳聞：「我個人的觀點是《魔戒》不適宜轉換成銀幕電影。那些認為我反對及敵視魔戒電影三部曲的言論是完全沒有根據的。」他又補充，他並沒有「表達這種情感」<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = BBC News | title = Tolkien's son denies rift | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/1697884.stm | date = 07-12-2001 | accessdate = 11-09-2009 | archive-date = 2009-03-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090315035516/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/1697884.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。魔戒小說的改編舞台音樂劇在2006年於[[多倫多|多倫多]]上演，但由於反應冷淡而結束。2007年夏季，該舞台音樂劇的縮短版在倫敦上演。魔戒電影三部曲的成功促使相關電腦遊戲及衍生商品的生產制作。

魔戒電影三部曲的成功使[[彼得·杰克逊|彼得·傑克森]]成為電影業界裡繼[[史提芬·史匹堡|史提芬·史匹堡]]及[[佐治·魯卡斯|佐治·魯卡斯]]後的佼佼者，與一些行內的重量級人物[[布萊恩·辛格|布萊恩·辛格]]、[[法蘭·達拉本特|法蘭·達拉本特]]及[[占士·金馬倫|占士·金馬倫]]齊名。傑克森成立了屬於他的電影公司溫紐特影片公司（Wingnut Films）及遊戲開發公司溫紐特工作室（Wingnut Interactive）<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | title = The World Machine： How Content Ruled the Ditigal Front | url = http://books.google.com.hk/books?id=IOsDAAAAMBAJ&pg=PT91#v=onepage&q=&f=false | journal = HWM | volume = 1 | pages = 第90頁 | year = 2007年 }}</ref>。2005年，傑克森得以重新制作《[[金剛_(2005年電影)|金剛]]》，雖然表現不如魔戒三部曲，但也取得不錯的票房收入。傑克森被稱為紐西蘭的「寵兒」<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = The New Zealand Herald | title = NZer of the year: Peter Jackson | url = http://www.nzherald.co.nz/lord-of-the-rings/news/article.cfm?c_id=594&objectid=584301 | date = 2001-12-29 | accessdate = 11-09-2009 | archive-date = 2018-07-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180719084312/https://www.nzherald.co.nz/lord-of-the-rings/news/article.cfm?c_id=594&objectid=584301 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2004年，霍華德·肖舉行《魔戒交響史詩》巡迴演出，每次演出長約兩小時<ref>''The Frodo Franchise: The Lord of the Rings and Modern Hollywood''，[http://books.google.com.hk/books?id=1odPDYvGBygC&pg=PA118#v=onepage&q=&f=false 第118頁]</ref>。魔戒電影三部曲及[[哈利波特|哈利波特]]振興了奇幻電影。魔戒三部曲以後，動作捕捉技術都被應用於《[[金剛_(2005年電影)|金剛]]》、《[[智能叛變|智能叛變]]》、《[[朱古力獎門人|朱古力獎門人]]》及《[[加勒比海盜：決戰魔盜王|加勒比海盜：決戰魔盜王]]》的角色上。魔戒電影所使用的虛擬環境多代理模擬系統（MASSIVE，一種高端電腦動畫及人工智能軟件）被其他的史詩式電影作品使用，包括《[[天國驕雄|天國驕雄]]》。魔戒電影三部曲帶動了紐西蘭的旅遊業，電影裡展示了紐西蘭的壯麗景色，吸引遊客慕名而來<ref>{{cite web |language=en |publisher=Cultural Travels |title=Movie Tourism in New Zealand |url=http://theculturedtraveler.com/Archives/AUG2005/Movies_New_Zeland.htm |author=Melissa Heath |accessdate=11-09-2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20051120164817/http://theculturedtraveler.com/Archives/AUG2005/Movies_New_Zeland.htm |archivedate=2005-11-20 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = Newzealand.com | title = Discover New Zealand, Home of Middle-earth | url = http://www.newzealand.com/travel/zhs/about-nz/features/lotr/lotr-02.cfm  | accessdate = 11-09-2009 }}</ref>。

魔戒電影三部曲所帶來的收益引起訴訟案件。十五名魔戒演員（諾埃爾·阿普萊比、傑德·布羅菲、馬克·法古臣、拉伊·亨伍德、布魯斯·霍普金斯、威廉·約翰遜、納旦尼爾·利斯、莎拉·麥克勞德、伊恩·穆內、保羅·諾瑞爾、克雷格·帕克、羅伯特·波洛克、馬田·桑德森、彼得·泰特及斯蒂芬·烏雷）提出起訴，指他們沒有從電影演出的相關產品得到應得的收益。案件在2008年審結，各演員獲得補償，然而諾埃爾·阿普萊比在2007因癌症逝世<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = TheOneRing.net | title = New Zealand actors settle out of court with New Line | url = http://www.theonering.net/torwp/2008/10/08/30205-new-zealand-actors-settle-out-of-court-with-new-line-cinema/ | author = MrCere | date = 08-10-2008 | accessdate = 11-09-2009 | archive-date = 2008-10-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081011115524/http://www.theonering.net/torwp/2008/10/08/30205-new-zealand-actors-settle-out-of-court-with-new-line-cinema/ | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。[[索爾·薩茲|索爾·薩茲]]在2004年亦提出訴訟，指他沒有收到全數的專利使用權費用。翌年，傑克森因利潤分成問題指控新線<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = Entertainment Weekly | title = 'The Hobbit': Peace in Middle-Earth? | url = http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20036782_20037403_20142132,00.html | author = Benjamin Svetkey | date = 04-10-2007 | accessdate = 11-09-2009 | archive-date = 2007-10-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20071005021459/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20036782_20037403_20142132%2C00.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。托爾金信託在2008年2月提出訴訟，指控新線拖欠應付的7.5%利潤分紅，索償1.5億美元<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = San Francisco Chronicle | title = Tolkien Estate Sues New Line Cinema | url = http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/n/a/2008/02/11/financial/f115544S35.DTL&tsp=1 | author = Alex Veiga | date = 12-02-2008 | accessdate = 11-09-2009 | archive-date = 2008-02-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080214055825/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fn%2Fa%2F2008%2F02%2F11%2Ffinancial%2Ff115544S35.DTL&tsp=1 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。法官否決了控方的懲罰性索償<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = BBC News | title = No punitive damages in Rings case | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/7637693.stm | accessdate = 11-09-2009 | archive-date = 2020-11-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201124220054/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/7637693.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>，但卻容許控方得到因新線違反合約的賠償。2009年9月8日，信托機構與新線達成和解（掃除了制作新電影《哈比人歷險記》的障礙）<ref>{{cite web | language = en | title = Legal settlement clears way for "Hobbit" movie | url = http://www.reuters.com/article/entertainmentNews/idUSTRE5875BK20090908 | publisher = Returns | accessdate = 11-09-2009 | archive-date = 2009-09-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090911142633/http://www.reuters.com/article/entertainmentNews/idUSTRE5875BK20090908 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

